## Specifications

* Built on [Meteor](https://www.meteor.com/) version 1.6.1
* Designed with [Webflow](https://www.webflow.com).

Check our [documentation](https://github.com/DemocracyEarth/sovereign/tree/master/docs) for technical reference.

